{
  "id": "RAW_edc62c78",
  "title": "NeurIPS 2025｜指哪打哪，可控对抗样本生成器来了！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651007352&idx=3&sn=81fcbd01f1d5e44813605a139fcd6b36",
  "date": "2025-12-15 08:07:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">近日，在全球人工智能领域最具影响力的顶级学术会议 NeurIPS（神经信息处理系统大会）上， 清华大学和蚂蚁数科联合提出了一种名为 Dual-Flow 的新型对抗攻击生成框架。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">简单来说，Dual-Flow 是一个能够从海量图像数据中学习 “通用扰动规律” 的系统，它不依赖目标模型结构、不需要梯度，却能对多种模型、多种类别发起黑盒攻击。其核心思想是通过 “前向扰动建模 — 条件反向优化” 的双流结构，实现对抗样本的高可迁移性与高成功率，同时保持极低的视觉差异。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">可以把它理解为一个“</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">可控的对抗样本生成器</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">”，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">只需指定想攻击的图像类别（如狗类、人类），模型就能自动生成该类别下逼真且有效的攻击图像</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，为 AI 安全带来了前所未有的挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523283\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4358974358974359\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"936\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7f09cfa1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibbOGibc3DIOqLQIeJlV7gYUFXn1o8DxQxWypycYyzQJaA238W4WcxaZCsMRiaUbXBkpzniaBbgpqq3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文标题：Dual-Flow: Transferable Multi-Target, Instance-Agnostic Attacks via In-the-wild Cascading Flow Optimization</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">作者：Yixiao Chen, Shikun Sun, Jianshu Li, Ruoyu Li, Zhe Li, Junliang Xing</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">机构：Tsinghua University, Ant Group</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文地址：<a href=\"https://openreview.net/pdf?id=zhCv5uZ8bh\" target=\"_blank\">https://openreview.net/pdf?id=zhCv5uZ8bh</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">GitHub：<a href=\"https://github.com/Chyxx/Dual-Flow\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Chyxx/Dual-Flow</a>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">研究背景与意义</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">随着 AI 模型在图像识别、自动驾驶、监控系统等领域广泛部署，“模型安全” 成为重要问题。尤其在黑盒环境下（攻击者无法知道模型结构和梯度），攻击通常依赖迁移性：希望一个方法能同时迷惑多个模型或多个类别。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">传统方法存在两大局限：</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">实例专属攻击（instance-specific）：高成功率，但只能针对单张图片，迁移性差。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通用生成器攻击（instance-agnostic）：迁移性有限，面对多目标、多模型时成功率下降。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">DualFlow 正是为了解决这些问题而提出的 —— 通过统一的生成优化框架，实现多目标、多模型、实例无关的高成功率攻击。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">⚡ 核心创新点</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">前向 + 反向 Flow 结构</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">DualFlow 并不在像素级别直接加噪声，而是：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">先把图片映射到 flow /latent 空间，在这个空间做结构化扰动</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">再通过 velocity function 反向映射到图像空间，生成对抗样本</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">相比传统 “像素扰动”，这种方法能生成更自然、更隐蔽、结构化的扰动，同时保持高迁移性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523287\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5889423076923077\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"832\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4ec1c4f0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibbOGibc3DIOqLQIeJlV7gYUK4SsJmQiabzRpsQ1CxC5sChw2ou91FfpRsqtXFSVHgBTgGB1ibJudyRw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多目标、实例无关攻击能力</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">DualFlow 的统一框架天然支持：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">多目标（multitarget）：一个生成器即可攻击多个类别</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">多模型（multimodel）：可迁移到不同架构的模型</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">实例无关（instanceagnostic）：无需针对特定图像训练</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这意味着，以往需要 “每个目标单独训练生成器” 的方法，现在只需一个生成器就能覆盖多个类别和模型，显著降低成本、提高实用性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">级联分布偏移训练（Cascading Distribution Shift Training）</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">训练过程中扰动分布逐步推进，使生成的对抗样本在不同时间步 / 中间表示上都能有效</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">大幅提升对多模型、多目标的迁移成功率</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">保证生成扰动在&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523312\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8846153846153846\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"52\" style=\"width:26px;height:23px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a1e4fdd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibbOGibc3DIOqLQIeJlV7gYU06BV7tNmvN5neibeBaUMvicIiaPsQ9FickaP3iaKibKqcbZKpGa3JJ0PeZAg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;约束下仍保持视觉隐蔽性</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523288\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5726495726495726\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"936\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=65f39d93&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibbOGibc3DIOqLQIeJlV7gYUybdibQd49icTicR9ibFaPxibt4wSZZnOxGBqLCbL3aM4x4hwB0GMKfsyraw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">📊 实验结果</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 ImageNet NeurIPS 验证集上对正常训练模型进行多目标攻击的成功率，扰动规模限制为&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523318\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24299065420560748\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"214\" style=\"width:94px;height:23px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5a72ee0b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibbOGibc3DIOqLQIeJlV7gYUpml0p8N5uCRyPAIv2OiavdtuZkxCrPQo4ByTO25ARjKyNzm9AB2uk8w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523290\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7051282051282052\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"936\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bf511e6a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibbOGibc3DIOqLQIeJlV7gYUV7g8grsPXjXWB4rywYibWGGoAIvcd9Yian6115Fzw5KewCepPlGQmMoA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 ImageNet 验证集上的实验表明，DualFlow 在单目标和多目标攻击中都展现了强大的迁移能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Table 2 显示，单目标攻击下，DualFlow 在黑盒环境中平均成功率明显高于传统方法，扰动幅度&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523317\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24299065420560748\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"214\" style=\"width:98px;height:24px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5a72ee0b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibbOGibc3DIOqLQIeJlV7gYUpml0p8N5uCRyPAIv2OiavdtuZkxCrPQo4ByTO25ARjKyNzm9AB2uk8w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;的情况下仍能显著误导模型；而白盒攻击下效果更佳。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5576923076923077\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"936\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=892dc6a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibbOGibc3DIOqLQIeJlV7gYUfl3mzl8Tj9kdvto0aBUlu4IDOWpaiaYUTqjgeRwichGwc1UMUgz8VX7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Table 3 进一步验证了 DualFlow 在多目标、多模型以及对抗训练模型上的迁移性能。结果显示，即使面对经过对抗训练的模型，DualFlow 依然保持较高成功率，体现了其在黑盒环境下的通用性和强大攻击力。整体来看，这些实验充分证明了 DualFlow 在实现多目标、多模型、实例无关攻击上的优势，同时在保证视觉隐蔽性的前提下，提供了现实环境下的高迁移攻击能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523293\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7606837606837606\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"936\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b13fe8cc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibbOGibc3DIOqLQIeJlV7gYUx47ibcrxJXd4EZcRQQicibznYkq1cYGBD0eZgD9kC9XW67bnDbpP4AWqw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此外，论文通过加入&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523315\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8846153846153846\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"52\" style=\"width:27px;height:24px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a1e4fdd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibbOGibc3DIOqLQIeJlV7gYU06BV7tNmvN5neibeBaUMvicIiaPsQ9FickaP3iaKibKqcbZKpGa3JJ0PeZAg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;约束限制像素级扰动，并利用 velocity 正则化让扰动在时间维度上更加平滑，使最终生成的视频几乎与原始视频无差别，但依然能够稳定让模型 “看走眼”。 &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523295\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8805309734513275\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"452\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3fd4e081&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibbOGibc3DIOqLQIeJlV7gYUnibfbG2jnqmD4SKby7YXlQhtTCod4xYXibiaKdAErub7ricujD1PxyN8fg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">总结与贡献</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Dual-Flow 提出了一种全新的通用对抗样本生成范式，通过前向与反向 Flow 的协同结构以及级联式分布偏移训练，实现了在多目标、多模型场景下依旧稳定有效的实例无关攻击。相比传统依赖像素级噪声的扰动方式，Dual Flow 所生成的扰动更具结构性、更难被察觉，同时一个生成器即可覆盖多个类别与模型，无需为每个攻击目标单独训练，大幅降低了使用成本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">实验结果表明，Dual-Flow 在黑盒条件下展现出极强的迁移性，例如在从 Inception-v3 迁移攻击 ResNet-152 的实验中，攻击成功率提升高达 34.58%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">该技术已经应用于蚂蚁数科身份安全相关产品的能力优化，集成了该对抗生成框架用于对抗样本的生成和检测，使得防御体系对对抗样本有更好的鲁棒性。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "清华大学与蚂蚁数科联合提出 Dual-Flow 框架，通过双流结构和级联分布偏移训练，实现高可迁移、多目标、实例无关的黑盒对抗样本生成。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "清华大学与蚂蚁数科联合提出 Dual-Flow 框架，通过双流结构和级联分布偏移训练，实现高可迁移、多目标、实例无关的黑盒对抗样本生成。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了一项在 NeurIPS 会议上发表的最新研究成果—— Dual-Flow 对抗攻击生成框架。该框架由清华大学和蚂蚁数科合作研发，旨在解决黑盒环境下对抗样本生成面临的迁移性差和成功率低等问题。Dual-Flow 创新性地采用“前向扰动建模—条件反向优化”的双流结构，实现了对抗样本的高可迁移性与高成功率，并在 flow/latent 空间进行结构化扰动而非直接像素扰动，生成更自然、隐蔽的对抗样本。同时，通过级联分布偏移训练大幅提升了对多模型、多目标的迁移成功率。实验结果表明，Dual-Flow 在黑盒环境中展现出远超传统方法的攻击成功率和通用性，且已应用于蚂蚁数科的身份安全产品能力优化中。",
